title: Royal Southern Brotherhood - Heartsoulblood [320k MP3]
description:
Royal Southern Brotherhood, Ruf Records' artists and 2014 Blues Music Awards winners, release their second studio CD, heartsoulblood on June 10, 2014 in the USA. Devon Allman, Cyril Neville, Mike Zito, Charlie Wooton and Yonrico Scott offer 12 original tracks that Cyril Neville describes as "Musical Gumbo." 

Royal Southern Brotherhood is an American blues and blues rock supergroup, consisting of singer and percussionist Cyril Neville, vocalist and guitarist Devon Allman, vocalist and guitarist Mike Zito, drummer Yonrico Scott, and bassist Charlie Wooton.
